front.title: •Why Does Everyone Want To Go Back To Jakku?!
front.gametext: Deploy on table. May deploy Lor San Tekka from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Once per turn, if you just lost a Resistance character from a Jakku site, may take a Resistance character of lesser ability into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)

pulledBy: We Wish To Board At Once
